        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2">
          <para styleclass="Notes">Notes:</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">To calculate <text styleclass="VariableName">Kinetostatic Forces Vectors</text>:</para>
          <list id="10" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">The <text styleclass="Body Text">kinematic-chain</text> is <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Kinematically-Defined-Chain">kinematically-defined</link>.</li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">A minimum of one <text styleclass="Element">Part</text> has <text styleclass="Body Text">mass</text>.</li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">The <text styleclass="Interface">Power Source</text> is configured to act at the correct <text styleclass="Element">Joint</text>, <text styleclass="Element">Cam</text>, <text styleclass="Element">Gear-Pair</text> or <text styleclass="Element">Spring</text> - see <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-Configure-Power-Source" styleclass="T_Menu">Configure Power Source</link><text styleclass="T_Menu"> dialog-box.</text></li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
